  <div class="phases">
    <div class="phase">
      <h3>Phase 1</h3>
      <p>Anchor Recruitment: 2â€“3 must-have anchors per RT. Personal outreach from Helix leadership.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="phase">
      <h3>Phase 2</h3>
      <p>Panel Composition: Build around anchors. Invitations say "You'll be in dialogue with X and Y."</p>
    </div>
    <div class="phase">
